<p>Good news: We found a donor to send you <i><%= @event.book %>!</i>
    <%= @event.donor.name %> in <%= @event.donor.location %>.
</p>

<% if @event.donation.address.present? %>
<% if !@event.donation.thanked? %>
<p><%= link_to "Send thanks to #{@event.donor.name}", new_donation_thank_url(@event.donation) %></p>
<% end %>

<p>Your book will arrive shortly. The address you gave was:</p>

<p>
<%= @event.donation.student.name %><br>
<%= format_address @event.donation.address %>
</p>

<p>You can <%= link_to 'update this info', request_url(@event.request) %> if needed.</p>
<% else %>
<p>However, you haven't given us your address! <%= link_to 'Add your address', fix_donation_flag_url(@event.donation) %> to get your book.
<% end %>
